<subSubSection id="131056D9E09E09E1D0D25452713498A9" pageId="null" pageNumber="351" type="vernacular_names">
<paragraph id="D6220ED98CF916DE2C8C8B9981126256" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">
<normalizedToken id="8CE18C4B9DA35C950F6FB9B6D11D2BFC" originalValue="Grasblättrige" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">Grasblaettrige</normalizedToken>
Skabiose
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="446AF62613764032B41206EE887BC48F" pageId="null" pageNumber="351" type="description">
<paragraph id="BBA50500C06998A1C60E3313E9AC99F9" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">
Ausdauernd, mit holzigem, verzweigtem Rhizom und zahlreichen sterilen Trieben; 20-50 cm hoch. Stengel aufsteigend, einfach und 
<normalizedToken id="50F9E5C0C310DFCB4F74EDEA643EE106" originalValue="einköpfig" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">einkoepfig</normalizedToken>
, im obern Teil dicht und anliegend behaart. 
<emphasis id="C62969DF90307C0FE16163F5DBD0A51B" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">
Alle 
<normalizedToken id="E60E3888F721892AD3F2473762BB2802" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
grasartig, 25
</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="230DFE48AB087BF7F92849AC57FDF270" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">100mal so lang wie breit, ganzrandig</emphasis>
, beiderseits dicht anliegend behaart. 
<normalizedToken id="7873EB30600A38C5457C3577713EB606" originalValue="Köpfe" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">Koepfe</normalizedToken>
3-4,5 cm im Durchmesser. 
<normalizedToken id="342A29807908B829C03C8D06BB0FA9E2" originalValue="Hüllblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">Huellblaetter</normalizedToken>
schmal lanzettlich, 
<normalizedToken id="D16E59459795228A84ECE3B402B15B20" originalValue="½" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">1/2</normalizedToken>
-⅔ so lang wie die 
<normalizedToken id="B861878F1D1A5ECFBE42EDA56E0902C6" originalValue="äußern" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">aeussern</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="89B88A16D16F6CE84A7A9BE53F9A5300" originalValue="Blüten" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">Blueten</normalizedToken>
. Kronen hellblauviolett. 
<emphasis id="98E2227D705A891D28197800E59955B4" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">
<normalizedToken id="5A55CE87D4AE015DE161D8A47C7766C7" originalValue="Außenkelch" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">Aussenkelch</normalizedToken>
2
</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="D6EAB4F0D50BD9FBEBFC7704DE808C9C" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">3,5 mm hoch</emphasis>
, 25-30nervig. Kelchborsten 3,5 bis 5 mm lang, gelblich. Frucht 3-4 mm lang, 
<emphasis id="A872B0BFAB6FDB8859BB62FF336571A8" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">
nur in der obern 
<normalizedToken id="9EF11736EE1E67C046545258B3C50A27" originalValue="Hälfte" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">Haelfte</normalizedToken>
8furchig, dicht und lang behaart
</emphasis>
(Haare ca. 2 mm lang). - 
<normalizedToken id="F12676C6B58A7FBE258FCD6FFE218146" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: 
<normalizedToken id="C64C37A8884DB9E37442CA4BEBBC6154" originalValue="Später" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">Spaeter</normalizedToken>
Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="FA37B8F90B5682255612DCF64D5A0AD0" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">
<emphasis id="38473F7D41CFE3BA58D9426158E3765C" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="ECC6CD6E5D82474FEE1FB160DA57EDF1" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">18:</emphasis>
Material aus botanischen 
<normalizedToken id="17AEC4F5BD9605382A120B806B97E1E0" originalValue="Gärten" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">Gaerten</normalizedToken>
(Kachidze 1929, Poucques 1949, Frey 1970). Sugiura (1943) 
<normalizedToken id="BEF60933BF06675CFEE0BDA50FF53E74" originalValue="zählte" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">zaehlte</normalizedToken>
an Material ohne Herkunftsangabe 
<emphasis id="99CF2BF46F2ABAB37A6BDECF9192AF4D" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="9185187B06235CA483ACE171E7F10DB4" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">16.</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="DFE895F94C1544A63446FA29C04ACF95" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">
<emphasis id="E65CEEA2B17666D9321D34D2F98EACD1" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">Standort.</emphasis>
Kollin und montan. Trockene, steinige 
<normalizedToken id="54150276EFE170865BF08F3C8719D91E" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">Boeden</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="D50B0F227E29CBBDB34F5705B68B20A3" originalValue="über" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">ueber</normalizedToken>
Kalk und Dolomit in warmen Lagen. Felsschutt, felsige 
<normalizedToken id="4EA6809BFFAE8B86AD6376504643EDFE" originalValue="Hänge" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">Haenge</normalizedToken>
und Grate.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="A24230611C28DE4BFB63516E1370C076" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">
<emphasis id="08F39373DA59E8756ABB55A667C5E174" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">
Verbreitung. Mittel- und 
<normalizedToken id="5F3B796EAD797573B4275FAC1828388B" originalValue="südeuropäische" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">suedeuropaeische</normalizedToken>
Gebirgspflanze
</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="229A296EE237C18EF05CAE86B701F5AC" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">
<normalizedToken id="7616DB95FDA2BB50EFFA2DDA15F86955" originalValue="südlich" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">suedlich</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
): 
<normalizedToken id="3E3BC853ED657F5AE3D380F0343DCAC2" originalValue="Pyrenäen" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">Pyrenaeen</normalizedToken>
, West- und 
<normalizedToken id="482848E39E1C7DEA99E35DE97FC3DC86" originalValue="Südalpen" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">Suedalpen</normalizedToken>
, Apennin (
<normalizedToken id="7AA0CE8BA9ADAD88126276E600EF580B" originalValue="südwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">suedwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis in die Abruzzen), Gebirge der Balkanhalbinsel (
<normalizedToken id="4343C88A54EB6A7157DC6529A1A9C8D5" originalValue="südwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">suedwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis Mazedonien). - Im Gebiet: Savoyen (Mont 
<normalizedToken id="CD5EEADB00FD26D75444C86A41E4089F" originalValue="Chauffé" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">Chauffe</normalizedToken>
), Valle 
<normalizedToken id="12F2AA248A37DC07D44F12EEB4F0DD8F" originalValue="d’Ossola" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">d'Ossola</normalizedToken>
(Valle Anzasca), 
<normalizedToken id="83EA2B7ACB7140FD09A949131439542E" originalValue="südliches" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">suedliches</normalizedToken>
Tessin, Comerseegebiet, Veltlin (Dubino, Gegend von Sondrio), 
<normalizedToken id="D2A058DEA205270AA3C7515F0D4B4EE6" originalValue="südliche" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">suedliche</normalizedToken>
Bergamasker Alpen.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
